public class ObjectPathfinder
extends Pathfinder

This subclass of Pathfinder searches for an object with a specific along the path from a starting point to a stopping point. Whereas Pathfinder places no restriction on the number or types of components that follow the , ObjectPathfinder allows only a version and segment number.
